title: D16.Group.VSTi.Pack.WiN(x86).(x64)-UNION
description:
D16 Group VSTi Pack Windows x86 and x64


Great vintage sounding plugins and drum machines. Easy to install and fully working.



Unpack all zip files.

Install each plugin- x86 or x64 based on which version DAW you have

Open VST in your DAW (might need to rescan)

Click activate when it says not yet registered

Find .reg file in original install folder and click ok

It should say registered to Union
